column5: Just a reminder, if you're planning on going to the Toronto Spring Fishing and Boat Show, that  Sunday morning at 730am we're having a great silent auction in conjunction with the 'Muskie' speakers!  Custom baits from Hosebait, Brett's Baits, Bare Bones Baits, lodge stays at Wolseley Lodge, Sandy Haven Camp. Guided fishing trips with Mike Parker, Frank DiMarcantonio, and Keith Davison.  Doors open at 730am, fishing show starts at 10am. Come spend a couple hours getting your Muskie fix!
Tickets available at the door Dax?  Cheers, Mark
Yes the doors open at 7 am you can get them there. Looking forward to the show. We will have show specials buy 4 baits get a free shirt. Stop by our booth after the musky Sunday seminars.
